0 ws0">人生几十年一晃就过了，<span class="_ _7"></span>若能在此期间播下解脱的种子，<span class="_ _7"></span>乃</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfc ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">至得到胸有成竹的解脱把握，这才是最重要的！ </div><div class="t m0 x5e h21 y239 ff15 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls54 ws0">（二） <span class="_ _1c"> </span><span class="ff16 ls0">问<span class="ffb fs3 ls55">：我是外交学院刚毕业的研究生。我在学</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y23a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">《中观庄严论释》<span class="_ _8"></span>时，<span class="_ _8"></span>看到麦彭仁波切反复讲<span class="_ _8"></span>“中观有无承</div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y23b ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls3f ws0">认否”<span class="_ _a"></span><span class="ls26">，说这是中观的一大难题，<span class="ls22">您讲课时也再三强调这个</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y5c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">问题很重要。<span class="_ _7"></span>但很多人可能都不明白它为何这么重要，<span class="_ _7"></span>能否</div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 y23c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">请您开示一下？ </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
